'''1950年NBA选秀'''（{{lang|en|1950 NBA draft}}）是[[国家篮球协会|国家篮球协会]]的第四届年度[[NBA选秀|选秀]]，这也是其从[[美国篮球协会|美国篮球协会]]变更为现名后的首届选秀。此次选秀与1950年4月25日举行。当时联盟的12支球队轮流从美国大学篮球业余运动员中选择队员加盟。每一轮中，各队按照前一赛季（1949-50赛季）的胜负成绩逆序选择球员。[[芝加哥牡鹿|芝加哥牡鹿]]参加了本次选秀，但是却在赛季开始之前宣告解散。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nba.com/bulls/history/stags_060417.html |title=Stag Party |last=Ballantini |first=Brett |work=NBA.com/Bulls |publisher=Turner Sports Interactive, Inc |date=2006-04-17 |accessdate=2009-10-30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091202022641/http://www.nba.com/bulls/history/stags_060417.html |archivedate=2009-12-02 |deadurl=no }}</ref>选秀共分12轮，有121名球员被选中。

== 选秀情况 ==
来自[[鮑林格林州立大學|鮑林格林州立大學]]的[[查克·谢尔|查克·谢尔]]被[[波士顿凯尔特人|波士顿凯尔特人]]选中，成为[[NBA选秀状元列表|状元新秀]]。[[维拉诺瓦大学|维拉诺瓦大学]]的[[保罗·阿里金|保罗·阿里金]]被[[金州勇士|费城勇士]]列为[[地緣選秀|地緣選秀]]对象。第六顺位新秀{{link-en|艾尔文·丹姆布拉特|Irwin Dambrot}}并没有在NBA打球，而是选择当一名牙医。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nytimes.com/1995/02/14/sports/sports-of-the-times-nat-holman-taught-team-basketball.html|title=Sports of The Times; Nat Holman 'Taught Team Basketball'|last=Anderson|first=Dave|work=NYTimes.com|publisher=The New York Times Company|date=1995-02-14|accessdate=2009-09-23|archive-date=2019-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190629010001/https://www.nytimes.com/1995/02/14/sports/sports-of-the-times-nat-holman-taught-team-basketball.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>该次选秀中共有4名球员入选[[奈史密斯篮球名人纪念堂|奈史密斯篮球名人纪念堂]]，他们是：[[保罗·阿里金|保罗·阿里金]]、[[鲍勃·库锡|鲍勃·库锡]]、[[乔治·亚德利|乔治·亚德利]]和[[比尔·沙尔曼|比尔·沙尔曼]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.basketball-reference.com/awards/hof.html|title=Naismith Memorial Basketball Hall of Fame Inductees|work=basketball-reference.com|publisher=Sports Reference LLC|date=|accessdate=2009-10-28|archive-date=2010-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101225151844/http://www.basketball-reference.com/awards/hof.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

第12顺位[[查克·库珀|查克·库珀]]和第100顺位[[厄尔·洛依德|厄尔·洛依德]]是首两位被NBA球队选中的[[非洲裔美国人|非洲裔美国人]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.seattlepi.com/basketball/303061_nban09.html|title=Inside the NBA: Black pioneers due respect|last=Washburn|first=Gary|work=Seattle Post-Intelligencer|publisher=Hearst Seattle Media, LLC|date=2007-02-09|accessdate=2010-05-24|archive-date=2012-10-05|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6BBQ6sSey?url=http://www.seattlepi.com/news/article/Inside-the-NBA-Black-pioneers-due-respect-1227823.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>1950年10月31日，洛依德成为首位在NBA中出场打球的非洲裔美国人，比库珀首秀早一天。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nba.com/sixers/community/earl_lloyd_050208.html|title=Earl Lloyd: A Basketball Pioneer|last=Ramsey|first=David|work=NBA.com/Sixers|publisher=Turner Sports Interactive, Inc|date=2005-02-16|accessdate=2009-09-23|archive-date=2012-10-05|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6BBQ7uS57?url=http://www.nba.com/sixers/community/earl_lloyd_050208.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.post-gazette.com/pg/09340/1018856-135.stm|title=Duquesne honors legacy of Chuck Cooper|last=Axelrod|first=Phil|work=Pittsburgh Post-Gazette|publisher=PG Publishing Co., Inc|date=2009-12-06|accessdate=2010-05-24|archive-date=2012-01-23|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/64tbw7x7Y?url=http://www.post-gazette.com/pg/09340/1018856-135.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

